Question: What do you like/dislike about public transportation.
Answer:
I actually have a personal vandetta against public transportation, at least the way it is run currently. In my experience of taking the bus, I have found it is rather unreliable. If you needed to be at a certain place at a specific time, you have to plan well in advance to make sure you get there, which is not always an option. But I do like that public transportation gives everyone a type of mobility they may not have had otherwise.